+
+| Dimension | Status | Notes |
+|-----------|--------|-------|
+| JSON Schema | **TRUSTED** | 939 lines, 16 tests pass; covers 10 game types |
+| GameRenderer trait | **TRUSTED** | `pipe_output()` contract exists; used by PipeMode |
